h1. {color:#6366f1}Prompt2Test{color} — Documentation Hub

{tip:title=AI-Powered Test Automation Platform}
QA engineers describe what they want to test in plain English — the AI agent authors a test plan, spins up a live browser, and executes it end-to-end. Built on AWS in *15 days* by *1 engineer*.
{tip}

