| {status:colour=Green|title=2} | [Architecture Diagram|02_ArchitectureDiagram] | Visual SVG system map with layers and data flows | Visual learners, presentations |
| {status:colour=Purple|title=3} | [Architecture Details|03_ArchitectureDetails] | Deep specs — services, config, IAM, cost, timing | Engineers, debugging |
| {status:colour=Yellow|title=4} | [Architecture Decisions|04_ArchitectureDecisions] | ADRs — why DynamoDB, Cognito Groups, Fargate, etc. | Architects, tech leads |
| {status:colour=Green|title=5} | [Deployment Guide|05_DeploymentGuide] | Step-by-step deploy to new AWS account | DevOps, initial setup |
| {status:colour=Red|title=6} | [CI/CD & Handover|06_CICDHandover] | Pipelines, day-to-day ops, troubleshooting | DevOps, on-call |
| {status:colour=Red|title=7} | [CAP Design Improvements|07_CAPDesign] | HA, consistency, partition tolerance — 4-tier plan | Architects, SRE |
| {status:colour=Green|title=8} | [Phase 2 Roadmap|08_Phase2Roadmap] | 7 features — promotion, retry, reports, ALB | Product owners, sprint planning |

