h2. Tech Stack

{section}
{column:width=25%}
h3. {color:#6366f1}Frontend{color}
* React 18
* TypeScript
* Vite
* AWS Amplify
* Tailwind-style inline
{column}
{column:width=25%}
h3. {color:#f97316}AI Agent{color}
* Python
* Strands SDK
* FastAPI
* Claude Sonnet 4.5
* Bedrock AgentCore
{column}
{column:width=25%}
h3. {color:#14b8a6}Backend / Data{color}
* Aurora Serverless v2
* PostgreSQL + pgvector
* DynamoDB
* RDS Data API
* Lambda (Python)
{column}
{column:width=25%}
h3. {color:#22c55e}Infrastructure{color}
* CDK (TypeScript)
* ECS Fargate
* CodePipeline
* Docker
* CloudFront
{column}
{section}

